{"tid":161850,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［識少少扮代表］食肉菌你知多少？","createTime":"2017-03-18T19:55:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-19T00:23:45.000Z","uid":23420,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"28c5f3fff28772d957feb2e0043855a87a7bab4a","tid":161850,"uid":23420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T19:55:52.000Z","msg":"首先食肉菌係一個統稱 唔係特指某一隻菌<br />\n當某d菌去左肌肉某一個位（筋膜）而個個位係白血球到唔到 咁d菌就可以Ba ba聲咁生 食埋你d肌肉 導致壞死性筋膜炎 咁就叫食肉菌 <br />\n由於依個病發病好快 同埋影響嚴重 所以一發現但趕唔切治療（應該話切除相應部份）隻菌就好易經筋膜散播到全身<br />\n<br />\n實際感染途徑真係唔清楚 <br />\n但應該真係好唔好彩d菌先經過重重關卡入到筋膜<br />\n<br />\n而常見食肉菌有好多 例如肺炎鏈球菌（Streptococcus pneumoniae) , 創傷弧菌 （Vibrio vulnificus) 當然仲有咩都關佢事既金黃葡萄球菌 (Staphylococcus aureus)<br />\n前者係正常存在係上呼吸道<br />\n創傷弧菌就係常見係海水到 所以點解話有傷口唔好游水好易中食肉菌 <br />\n因此食肉菌唔係淨係海水先會惹到<br />\n<br />\n但近排有單比較罕見既係 有個伯伯係條頸有食肉菌而個隻係XX乳桿菌(lactobacillus) 而依種菌係化驗個時好多時都當左係commensal (正常存在係人體既菌）或者當contaminant  所以實在好罕見<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170312/mobile/bkn-20170312000029395-0312_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170312%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20170312000029395-0312_00822_001.html&d=A2ufI7QLpLp1ny1o1CjT3m6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=2a552604\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170312/mobile/bkn-20170312000029395-0312_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n有咩關於菌/病毒既簡單野可以問下<br />\n唔好估估下又話咩新SARS 咩醫療倒退50年 不才會盡力解答<br />\n或者睇睇以下wiki有唔明再問<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/坏死性筋膜炎\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E5%9D%8F%E6%AD%BB%E6%80%A7%E7%AD%8B%E8%86%9C%E7%82%8E&d=A2ufI7QLpLp1ny1o1CjT3m6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=5e8bbb27\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/坏死性筋膜炎</a><br />\n唔好屌條link殘體 我都唔想<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：非醫生 識少少microbiology野 有錯請指正"},{"pid":"4b624f82410f4a7066311b4615d5ff22b85bffeb","tid":161850,"uid":14872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T19:59:24.000Z","msg":"家用廁所水都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n彈到係咪死硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17d6c93ffa6131dc150990c11ddf2af1d3ab9997","tid":161850,"uid":14872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T20:02:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1370679059544f3c78d665e8a10dc36defb76a03","tid":161850,"uid":14872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T20:03:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90ad6744a01cfb3b616a5a083ad8dec6ebc6810f","tid":161850,"uid":23420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T20:08:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>家用廁所水都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n彈到係咪死硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n實際上廁所水入面一定有好撚好撚多種菌<br />\n如果個d菌可以係你身體內繁殖（特別係筋膜）應該都可以搖身一變變「食肉菌」 <br />\n但其實廁所水入面有咩致病菌真係唔太清楚 <br />\n而以上提及既常見食肉菌比較少會出現係廁所水<br />\n所以我覺得廁所水到感染既機會唔大（個人揣測）<br />\n<br />\n彈到一定唔係死硬<br />\n首先你會感染食肉菌個原理就係 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">某隻菌去到筋膜再繁殖到</span><br />\n菌去筋膜 中間其實有好多重關卡<br />\nEg 你既皮膚，皮膚下面又有幾層，血液入面既白血球<br />\n所以菌去到筋膜真係要過五關斬六將<br />\n<br />\n當然如果你有傷口 自然少左幾層保護又會易感染d <br />\n所以如果你有傷口彈到都可以驚一驚 但好人好者彈到又怕咩呢"},{"pid":"e4f040e2c9ed19ad2d2935e0454ba7c5e90b8262","tid":161850,"uid":14872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T20:11:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>家用廁所水都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n彈到係咪死硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n實際上廁所水入面一定有好撚好撚多種菌<br />\n如果個d菌可以係你身體內繁殖（特別係筋膜）應該都可以搖身一變變「食肉菌」 <br />\n但其實廁所水入面有咩致病菌真係唔太清楚 <br />\n而以上提及既常見食肉菌比較少會出現係廁所水<br />\n所以我覺得廁所水到感染既機會唔大（個人揣測）<br />\n<br />\n彈到一定唔係死硬<br />\n首先你會感染食肉菌個原理就係 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">某隻菌去到筋膜再繁殖到</span><br />\n菌去筋膜 中間其實有好多重關卡<br />\nEg 你既皮膚，皮膚下面又有幾層，血液入面既白血球<br />\n所以菌去到筋膜真係要過五關斬六將<br />\n<br />\n當然如果你有傷口 自然少左幾層保護又會易感染d <br />\n所以如果你有傷口彈到都可以驚一驚 但好人好者彈到又怕咩呢</blockquote><br />\n有傷囗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知自己有冇感染<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16e2fe4228a7f2af948a9fcb25f505760c9a07ca","tid":161850,"uid":23420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T20:14:52.000Z","msg":"［quote]有傷囗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知自己有冇感染<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[/quote]<br />\n<br />\n早期症狀為皮膚紅腫、發熱、變硬，腫脹呈紫紅色片狀，邊界不清，且伴有強烈疼痛感。病人可伴有流感症狀，包括發熱、寒顫、腹瀉、嘔吐、四肢無力、心動過速及肌肉酸痛。"},{"pid":"a7a93777e7c5abfce3ae6b652a85cfd4204c357f","tid":161850,"uid":23420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T20:15:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\"><blockquote>［quote]有傷囗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知自己有冇感染<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></span><br />\n<br />\n早期症狀為皮膚紅腫、發熱、變硬，腫脹呈紫紅色片狀，邊界不清，且伴有強烈疼痛感。病人可伴有流感症狀，包括發熱、寒顫、腹瀉、嘔吐、四肢無力、心動過速及肌肉酸痛。[/quote]<br />\n<br />\nFail"},{"pid":"9ada4b0080a986b3007fff1b0dd7f5ef1bb78a5a","tid":161850,"uid":31923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T20:15:34.000Z","msg":"有次浮潛比珊瑚界到隻腳流血 <br />\n係咪算好彩.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9e3239ca0fa9ac0f2cb9f2af55a1ac6ed79ebc6","tid":161850,"uid":14872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T20:17:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: violet;\"><blockquote>［quote]有傷囗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知自己有冇感染<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></span><br />\n<br />\n早期症狀為皮膚紅腫、發熱、變硬，腫脹呈紫紅色片狀，邊界不清，且伴有強烈疼痛感。病人可伴有流感症狀，包括發熱、寒顫、腹瀉、嘔吐、四肢無力、心動過速及肌肉酸痛。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nFail[/quote]<br />\n冇痛 應該冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cacae1eeeb8272afa9ddf38b4860a0a221c170e0","tid":161850,"uid":14065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T21:23:38.000Z","msg":"病入膏肓<br />\n膏肓係咪指筋膜？"},{"pid":"4fac172752c6508c01630c099b20d4f4bf9dba61","tid":161850,"uid":2192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T21:50:03.000Z","msg":"咩叫邊界不清？"},{"pid":"e3ecf34aa509cb15ff4f1b776c3b0226d3fa9bf4","tid":161850,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T23:03:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我唔練肌肉之餘再用脂肪包住佢並唔係冇原因"},{"pid":"717a0467a24413e73a3f14b30a4ff7ae04dcb57b","tid":161850,"uid":37525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T23:52:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>家用廁所水都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n彈到係咪死硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n實際上廁所水入面一定有好撚好撚多種菌<br />\n如果個d菌可以係你身體內繁殖（特別係筋膜）應該都可以搖身一變變「食肉菌」 <br />\n但其實廁所水入面有咩致病菌真係唔太清楚 <br />\n而以上提及既常見食肉菌比較少會出現係廁所水<br />\n所以我覺得廁所水到感染既機會唔大（個人揣測）<br />\n<br />\n彈到一定唔係死硬<br />\n首先你會感染食肉菌個原理就係 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">某隻菌去到筋膜再繁殖到</span><br />\n菌去筋膜 中間其實有好多重關卡<br />\nEg 你既皮膚，皮膚下面又有幾層，血液入面既白血球<br />\n所以菌去到筋膜真係要過五關斬六將<br />\n<br />\n當然如果你有傷口 自然少左幾層保護又會易感染d <br />\n所以如果你有傷口彈到都可以驚一驚 但好人好者彈到又怕咩呢</blockquote><br />\n嘩 咁我想問<br />\n如果放支牙刷 比廁所水/其他菌 彈到<br />\n有牙周病 刷牙流牙血 有傷口<br />\n咁中唔中？會唔會經牙肉上腦？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72b2ae4038b622460ecefaee009bc00ae3fe5901","tid":161850,"uid":31920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T23:54:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我唔練肌肉之餘再用脂肪包住佢並唔係冇原因</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  呢為巴打所言甚是"},{"pid":"c0d913f6f47dd861361fce37554967a0d112e491","tid":161850,"uid":24280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T00:04:39.000Z","msg":"lm學野"},{"pid":"5aa92df4ee174f17dac2f7bbd7d81e8fe89fa05e","tid":161850,"uid":48065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T00:11:04.000Z","msg":"好驚 手有傷口 掂過廁所水"},{"pid":"386880ef4c891a58e45ee862faa1891f1d9a6628","tid":161850,"uid":48065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T00:14:04.000Z","msg":"其實拎你地部手機去種菌 應該都好多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c45ec302f3d820bb39b22a3b6e8a85d05f8ee577","tid":161850,"uid":31752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T00:17:03.000Z","msg":"中招機率同六合彩比邊個高?"},{"pid":"0f9caacfa8bc8bfef830f9d08dae4979cbdd1c5b","tid":161850,"uid":59684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T00:23:45.000Z","msg":"之前游水比石頭界傷 好彩無事"}]}